The experimental design was a randomized complete block design (regular), in a 7 Ã— 2 + 1 factorial scheme, corresponding to (i) seven sorghum and grasses intercrops (Andropogon gayanus - AG; Cenchrus ciliaris cv. aridus - CCA; Cenchrus ciliaris cv. 131 - CC; Brachiaria decumbens - BD; Brachiaria brizantha - BB; Brachiaria ruziziensis - B R; Panicum maximum Jacq - PM), two planting-row spacings (0.4 or 0.8 m), (iii) plus an additional treatment of sorghum without grasses (check-plot). 
